f Defence  of the  Kingdom of Norway (\"NMOD\") and Gripen International AB (\"GI\"), a business  unit of Saab AB  (publ), hereinafter jointly referred to as the \"Parties\" and individually referred to as \"Party\".", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 0, "end_char_idx": 339, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "a5c82e1e-9fb0-49c1-b72d-a90830c6fb33": {"__data__": {"id_": "a5c82e1e-9fb0-49c1-b72d-a90830c6fb33", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "b94006ef-cdb8-4836-a692-24d96871b11b", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "78bd724070eefb11d412048db3d18c2cf7dcd6bd9bf2d8df803917fab0209f66", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "eca1f411-0319-43b9-8054-9b03e878b461", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "46acc620298a7a5bd99795628c324989b362816f178090d14757647f3640155d", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "61023d28-e215-4d92-bce2-8975149f1d35", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "047d1f558c7a9b2fee884a6b53d66b6d3d22fed0567b48d7a509510166a3857a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The  Parties:\n\nare referring to the letter of agreement between NMOD and GI concerning industrial participation in further development of Gripen and related projects (the \"LOA\");\n\nnoting their wish to exchange  information  for the  purpose of conducting evaluations  of the Gripen aircraft,\n\n  and  pursuing discussions  and work related to the Gripen  Demonstrator  Programme  and other Gripen and defence  related projects (\"LOA Projects\");", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 339, "end_char_idx": 782, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "61023d28-e215-4d92-bce2-8975149f1d35": {"__data__": {"id_": "61023d28-e215-4d92-bce2-8975149f1d35", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "b94006ef-cdb8-4836-a692-24d96871b11b", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "78bd724070eefb11d412048db3d18c2cf7dcd6bd9bf2d8df803917fab0209f66", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "a5c82e1e-9fb0-49c1-b72d-a90830c6fb33", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "cae06d2bd0c9a2c9b516be06a887214a5236a092b22854399e13a9881a0486e8", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "c1949424-fbd1-4398-a6bc-c128aec570ff", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d004ce834b50d8a9b46b0bbb5171f68976c49523200377f3efce4bcb953a2ab6", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "noting that such exchange  of information  may involve the disclosure  of confidential  information  by either  Party,\n\n and that the  Parties wish to record their agreement  to maintain the confidentiality  of such information;", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 784, "end_char_idx": 1012, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "c1949424-fbd1-4398-a6bc-c128aec570ff": {"__data__": {"id_": "c1949424-fbd1-4398-a6bc-c128aec570ff", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "b94006ef-cdb8-4836-a692-24d96871b11b", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "78bd724070eefb11d412048db3d18c2cf7dcd6bd9bf2d8df803917fab0209f66", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "61023d28-e215-4d92-bce2-8975149f1d35", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "047d1f558c7a9b2fee884a6b53d66b6d3d22fed0567b48d7a509510166a3857a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "0a908ce5-b316-4291-b7e0-063d90dd7809", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "8ed7bde9f5106fd4e1269b7e73d0a4bce19843d667003367c6d3a750ea922260", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "noting that exchanging  information with  GI shall also include exchanging information  with  Saab and upon such disclosure  Saab shall confirm  and be bound of the terms and conditions  contained  herein as if Saab was a Party to the  NDA;", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1014, "end_char_idx": 1254, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "0a908ce5-b316-4291-b7e0-063d90dd7809": {"__data__": {"id_": "0a908ce5-b316-4291-b7e0-063d90dd7809", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "b94006ef-cdb8-4836-a692-24d96871b11b", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "78bd724070eefb11d412048db3d18c2cf7dcd6bd9bf2d8df803917fab0209f66", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "c1949424-fbd1-4398-a6bc-c128aec570ff", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "d004ce834b50d8a9b46b0bbb5171f68976c49523200377f3efce4bcb953a2ab6", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "a979ed97-22e7-458f-84d4-96e806d7b3fd", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9363ed950730740da8e504043c499ca1b8d1b5cb9625d04c1117e273863dd328", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "noting that  exchanging  information with the  NMOD shall also include other  Norwegian authorities  and upon such disclosure  said Norwegian authority  shall confirm  and be bound of the terms and conditions contained  herein as if said Norwegian authority was a Party to the  NDA.\n\nNOW, THEREFORE,", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1256, "end_char_idx": 1555, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "a979ed97-22e7-458f-84d4-96e806d7b3fd": {"__data__": {"id_": "a979ed97-22e7-458f-84d4-96e806d7b3fd", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "b94006ef-cdb8-4836-a692-24d96871b11b", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "78bd724070eefb11d412048db3d18c2cf7dcd6bd9bf2d8df803917fab0209f66", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "0a908ce5-b316-4291-b7e0-063d90dd7809", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "8ed7bde9f5106fd4e1269b7e73d0a4bce19843d667003367c6d3a750ea922260", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "ead7cc38-867f-4b6f-b3bb-d302ddd2a030", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9aed8bab792aa2cba49625b86ef5f4f107caed7bfc30c6254a8b155ae63a415a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "the parties agree as follows:\n\nClause 1\n\nConfidential  Information  - information  of whatever  kind and  in whatever  form contained  (and includes  in particular  but without  prejudice to the generality  of the foregoing,  documents,  drawings, computerized  information,  films,  tapes, specifications,  designs,  models,", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1557, "end_char_idx": 1882, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "ead7cc38-867f-4b6f-b3bb-d302ddd2a030": {"__data__": {"id_": "ead7cc38-867f-4b6f-b3bb-d302ddd2a030", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "b94006ef-cdb8-4836-a692-24d96871b11b", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "78bd724070eefb11d412048db3d18c2cf7dcd6bd9bf2d8df803917fab0209f66", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "a979ed97-22e7-458f-84d4-96e806d7b3fd", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9363ed950730740da8e504043c499ca1b8d1b5cb9625d04c1117e273863dd328", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "544596a1-9a9e-4c46-866f-bfec6207104c", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "65e9f3754d88c3d2acfa2dd3f3eb9f861a86aed8f1cbfc8fab1b42644083566d", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "equipment  or data of any kind) which  is clearly identified  by the  Disclosing  Party as confidential  by an appropriate  legend or if orally disclosed then  upon disclosure  or within  30 days of such oral disclosure identified  in writing  by the  Disclosing  Party as confidential.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1883, "end_char_idx": 2169, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "544596a1-9a9e-4c46-866f-bfec6207104c": {"__data__": {"id_": "544596a1-9a9e-4c46-866f-bfec6207104c", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "b94006ef-cdb8-4836-a692-24d96871b11b", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "78bd724070eefb11d412048db3d18c2cf7dcd6bd9bf2d8df803917fab0209f66", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "ead7cc38-867f-4b6f-b3bb-d302ddd2a030", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "9aed8bab792aa2cba49625b86ef5f4f107caed7bfc30c6254a8b155ae63a415a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "033a7520-6214-4907-84fb-35e3fa165762", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "72e45f50f353bb6459a8ec04f4f19290ec81b21ba08dcac1d74cdec66dcd8d03", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Disclosing  Party  - the  party from time to time disclosing  Confidential Information.1\nReceiving  Party  - the  party from time to time  receiving Confidential  Information.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2171, "end_char_idx": 2346, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "033a7520-6214-4907-84fb-35e3fa165762": {"__data__": {"id_": "033a7520-6214-4907-84fb-35e3fa165762", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "b94006ef-cdb8-4836-a692-24d96871b11b", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "78bd724070eefb11d412048db3d18c2cf7dcd6bd9bf2d8df803917fab0209f66", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "544596a1-9a9e-4c46-866f-bfec6207104c", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "65e9f3754d88c3d2acfa2dd3f3eb9f861a86aed8f1cbfc8fab1b42644083566d", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "556a8a75-9994-40d0-80e0-b4a905a8b3f5", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "1916d9e8251b6b9745464c1674cf57482a7ecb387f38d2c26016707b929d25ea", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Clause 2\n\nSubject  to the terms of the  NDA the Receiving Party hereby undertakes  to the Disclosing  Party:\n\na) that it shall treat the Confidential  Information directly or indirectly disclosed to it by the  Disclosing  Party as strictly confidential  and will  not without obtaining  the  prior written  consent  of the  Disclosing  Party disclose  any part of the Confidential  Information to any third  party,", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2348, "end_char_idx": 2762, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "556a8a75-9994-40d0-80e0-b4a905a8b3f5": {"__data__": {"id_": "556a8a75-9994-40d0-80e0-b4a905a8b3f5", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "b94006ef-cdb8-4836-a692-24d96871b11b", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "78bd724070eefb11d412048db3d18c2cf7dcd6bd9bf2d8df803917fab0209f66", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "033a7520-6214-4907-84fb-35e3fa165762", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "72e45f50f353bb6459a8ec04f4f19290ec81b21ba08dcac1d74cdec66dcd8d03", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "27915ce5-f103-4fc8-be17-9fa0cdde4ea8", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "49d22289d30811b69921ec1d278237756bc6971c241071f238deaa9067344283", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "except where  compelled by law or regulation;\n\nb) that it shall not make  use of any part of  the Confidential Information disclosed to it by the Disclosing Party,\n\n  except  for  LOA purposes;\n\nc) that it shall give access to the  Confidential  Information only,", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2765, "end_char_idx": 3028, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "27915ce5-f103-4fc8-be17-9fa0cdde4ea8": {"__data__": {"id_": "27915ce5-f103-4fc8-be17-9fa0cdde4ea8", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "b94006ef-cdb8-4836-a692-24d96871b11b", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "78bd724070eefb11d412048db3d18c2cf7dcd6bd9bf2d8df803917fab0209f66", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "556a8a75-9994-40d0-80e0-b4a905a8b3f5", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "1916d9e8251b6b9745464c1674cf57482a7ecb387f38d2c26016707b929d25ea", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "91e6a755-4dfd-4fb5-9a58-ca2eb4f8a3be", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "c3238b452cbd73dedc7f066ae6e9079786a6050b1c3e0edb9e9d01a548ec23a0", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "to those of its employees who need access to the Confidential Information for  LOA purposes and will ensure that  such  employees adhere to the obligations and restrictions contained in the NDA;\n\nd) that it shall  not copy or reproduce  in any form  any of the Confidential Information  disclosed  to it by the  Disclosing  Party,\n\n except to the extent necessary for the  LOA purposes;", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3030, "end_char_idx": 3416, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "91e6a755-4dfd-4fb5-9a58-ca2eb4f8a3be": {"__data__": {"id_": "91e6a755-4dfd-4fb5-9a58-ca2eb4f8a3be", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "b94006ef-cdb8-4836-a692-24d96871b11b", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "78bd724070eefb11d412048db3d18c2cf7dcd6bd9bf2d8df803917fab0209f66", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "27915ce5-f103-4fc8-be17-9fa0cdde4ea8", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "49d22289d30811b69921ec1d278237756bc6971c241071f238deaa9067344283", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "3739546f-c81e-4261-9157-79ff165b99dc", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "53bd6c820d91341dd68a854d68c9801ab7d003a95e494fb1738d9ee190fcefa4", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "and\n\ne) that it shall  keep a current  record of all copies and reproductions  of the Confidential  Information.\n\nClause 3\n\nThe  obligations  under the  NDA do  not apply to information  of the  Disclosing Party which  is:\n\na) at the time of disclosure  or thereafter  available to the  public generally through  no failure  on the  part of the  Receiving Party;", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3418, "end_char_idx": 3780, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "3739546f-c81e-4261-9157-79ff165b